MOIS01 Turnaround Times

Period: Since June 1st, 2017

  A total of 7803 samples were received. Of these 7803 were completed. The remainder are either in progress or were cancelled.

The samples came from 90 separate customers.

 

Breakdown of times

 

 

 

 

Summary Data (Days)

  • Transit = time from being logged to being received.
  • Prep = time from receipt to release from sample prep.
  • Waiting = time from being released from sample prep to being started.
  • Test_Time = time from being started to being completed.
  • Checked = time from being completed to being reviewed.
  • Review = time to be reviewed once released.
  • TAT = time from being logged to being reviewed.
